      "QUESTION_1": "How can I register on the platform?",
      "ANSWER_1": "To register, click the 'Sign Up' button at the top of the page. Complete the form with your personal and business information. Once submitted, you will receive a confirmation email to activate your account.",
      "QUESTION_2": "What features are included in my free account?",
      "ANSWER_2": "The free account includes basic access to coffee batch recording, basic supplier management and coffee defect consultation. For advanced features like detailed analytics and custom reports, you can upgrade to a premium plan.",
      "QUESTION_3": "How can I recover my password?",
      "ANSWER_3": "On the login page, click 'Forgot your password?' Enter your registered email and we will send you a link to reset your password. Follow the instructions in the email to create a new password.",
      "QUESTION_4": "Can I change my subscription plan at any time?",
      "ANSWER_4": "Yes, you can upgrade or change your subscription plan at any time from your account settings. Changes will be applied immediately and billing will be prorated accordingly.",
      "QUESTION_5": "How can I contact technical support?",
      "ANSWER_5": "You can contact us through this form, by sending an email to contacto@cafelab.com, via WhatsApp at +51 912 345 678, or through our LinkedIn profile. Our office hours are Monday to Friday from 9:00 a.m. to 6:00 p.m."
    }
